sum of elements of array::
sum = 0
    for i in arr:
        sum=sum+i
    return sum 
    


You will be given an integer n, your task is to return the sum of all natural number less than or equal to n.
    return (n*(n+1)//2)%1000000007



Binary Search :
	def binarysearch(self, arr, n, k):
		# code here
		i=0
		t=False
		while not(t) and i<n:
		    if arr[i]==k:
		        t=True
		    else:
		        i+=1
        if t:
            return i
        else:
            return -1
    
